  <description>
    <p>Tauon is a modern, comfortable and streamlined music player for the playback of your music collection.</p>
    <p>Packed with features while maintaining simplicity. Use drag and drop for easy file importing and playlist management. Groups albums by folder and allows you to manage your music with built-in functions such as file and folder renaming, cover art downloading and file deleting.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Playback local audio files including MP3, FLAC and OGG</li>
      <li>Import Spotify tracks and manage Spotify playlists</li>
      <li>Add network tracks from Jellyfin, Airsonic and Plex servers</li>
      <li>Gapless playback</li>
      <li>Automatic CUE sheet detection</li>
      <li>Lookup artists on Rate Your Music and Bandcamp</li>
      <li>Support for last.fm and Listenbrainz</li>
      <li>Import downloaded music archives in one click</li>
      <li>Large album art and gallery layouts</li>
      <li>Support for lyrics including synced lrc files and guitar chords</li>
      <li>Multiple preset colour themes</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

